 his work was published in the comic anthology rock ink rollsandberg has been teaching character animation at mcad since  and has been a graduate mentor since  over the years he has also been an exhibiting painter and a lifelong student of anatomy and figure drawing related posts student profile senior amanda mitchell garcias tedx talk on how to be a verb search form search mcad calendar all events july –september  armin hofmann farbecolor july –august  in transit july –august  crossing the line drawing practices for and with the older adult august –september  tone poems of color makemcad academic programsundergraduatemajorsanimationcomic artdrawing and paintingentrepreneurial studiesfilmmakingfine arts studiofurniture designgraphic designillustrationphotographyprint paper bookproduct designsculptureweb and multimedia environmentsminorsart historycreative writingteaching artistfoundation studiesliberal artsgraduatemaster of fine artsvisual studiesmaster of artssustainable designpostbaccalaureatepostbaccalaureate certificatesgraphic designinteractive design and marketingprecollegeprecollege programspostsecondary enrollment option pseoprecollege summer sessionadmissions and aidundergraduateundergraduate admissionstuition and feesapplication checklistdates and deadlinestransferring creditapply for admissionfinancial aidtypes of aidaid eligibilityapply for aidnet cost calculatorgraduatemaster of arts admissionstuition and feesapplication checklistdates and deadlinesmaster of fine arts admissionstuition and feesapplication checklistdates and deadlinesfinancial aidtypes of aidaid eligibilityapply for aidpostbaccalaureategraphic design certificate admissionstuition and feesapplication checklistdates and deadlinesinteractive design and marketing admissionstuition and feesapplication checklistdates and deadlinesapply for admissionfinancial aidtypes of aidaid eligibilityapply for aidprecollegeprecollege summer sessionapplication requirementsdates and deadlinesscholarshipspost